“Chong2-si7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 , I hou7 lan2 tui3 lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok tit-tioh8 khah-iaN5” (I Ko-lim5-to 15:57). Choe3 chit8-e5 Ki-tok-tou5, te7-it pi-siong e5 keng-giam7 chiu7-si7 choe7 e5 chun5-chai7 kap i e5 koan5-se3. Kin-a2-jit8 u7 Lo5-ma2 Jin5-su te7 8 chiuN sou2 ki3-chai3 koan5-soaN-teng2 e5 seng-oah8, bin5-a2-jit8 to3-tng2 kau3 Lo5-ma2 Jin5-su te7 7 chiuN sou2 kong2 chhin-chhiuN7 soaN-kok e5 seng-oah8; kin-a2-jit8 ti7 eng3-un2 e5 toe7 tek-seng3, bin5-a2-jit8 beh to3-tng2 kau3 khong3-ia2 keng-ke3 sit-pai7 e5 seng-oah8,------che chiu7-si7 goa2 sou2 teh kong2 te7-it pi-siong e5 keng-giam7.
