Ap-che3 Choe7-ok Kap Bo5 Choe7 E5 Oan5-choan5
Ap-che3 choe7-ok a2-si7 tu5-khi3 choe7-ok e5 pun2-seng3, hit nng7-ku3 oe7 long2 bo5 ki3-chai3 ti7 Seng3-keng, sou2-i2 goa2 bo5 beh kong2 i. Goa2 kam-goan7 hou7 goa2 e5 siuN7-hoat u7 chho3-gou7, ia7 bo5 beh hou7 goa2 e5 sim u7 m7-tioh8; goa2 kam-goan7 hou7 goa2 e5 li2-lun7 u7 chho3-gou7, ia7 m7-ai3 goa2 e5 sou2 choe3 u7 m7-tioh8. Goa2 beh choe3 chit8-e5 tek-seng3 e5 Ki-tok-tou5.
Tak8-pai2 goa2 na7 siuN7 tioh8 ap-che3 choe7-ok, goa2 chiu7 siuN7 tioh8 chit8-e5 kou3-su7. U7 chit8-e5 Kui3-keh-hoe7 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5 , ti7 i chin siu7-khi3 e5 si5, iau2-ku2 oe7 thang bin7 u7 chhio3-iong5. U7 chit8-e5 chheng-lian5 lang5 mng7 i kong2: Goa2 sit8-chai7 boe7 beng5-pek8, ti7 chit khoan2 cheng5-heng5 li2 iau2 oe7 thun-lun2 bo5 siu7-khi3. Chit-e5 ka-ki7 liah8-choe3 chai-iaN2 tek-seng3 pi3-koat e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5 ka7 i kong2: Chong2-si7 li2 bo5 khoaN3 tioh8 goa2 sim-lai7 moa2-pak e5 siu7-khi3.
Bo5-lun7 khoaN3 oe7 tioh8, a2-si7 un2-bat8 ti7 sim-lai7 e5, long2 kang7-khoan2 si7 siu7-khi3. Sui-jian5 li2 oe7 ap-che3 i, bo5 hou7 pat8-lang5 khoaN3 tioh8, chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 long2 u7 khoaN3 tioh8; kau3 u7 chit8 jit8 hiah-e5 siu7-khi3 long2 beh lou7-hian7. Li2 e5 siu7-khi3 bo5-lun7 si7 khoaN3 oe7 tioh8, a2-si7 un2-bat8 ti7 lai7-bin7, hoan7-na7 siu7-khi3, chiu7 m7-si7 tek-seng3.
Koh u7 chit8-e5 kou3-su7. U7 nng7 e5 gin2-na2 teh sio-ian2, chong2-si7 hou7 lang5 siuN7 boe7 kau3, hit-e5 soe3-han3 e5 ian2-to2 pi2 i khah toa7-han3 e5, koh khia5 ti7 i e5 teng2-bin7. Khia7 ti7 piN-a2 e5 lang5 mng7 kong2: Li2 i2-keng iaN5 i lah, siaN2-su7 iau2-ku2 khia5 ti7 i e5 seng-khu, m7 hou7 i khi2-lai5 nih? Hit e5 gin2-na2 kong2: Goa2 u7 kam2-kak tioh8 i chun2-pi7 beh hoan-sin khi2-lai5 ian2 goa2. HiaN-ti7 chi2-be7, Chu2 Ia5-sou oe7 thau2-pang3 li2, hou7 li2 lai7-bin7 e5 choe7 bo5 ka2-kun2, boe7 hoan-sin khi2-lai5.
Ki-tok-kau3 Soan-to7-hoe7 e5 chhong3-pan7-jin5, Soan-sin3 Phok-su7 (Dr. A. B. Simpson) an2-ni kong2: Ti7 Ia5-sou u7 it-chhe3 e5 hong-seng7, Ia5-sou si7 it-chhe3. U7 choe7-choe7 lang5 teh siuN7, sin3 to7-li2 chiu7 oe7 tek-seng3, na7-si7 au7-lai5 chiah chai, tek-seng3 si7 ti7 Chu2 Ia5-sou, chiu7 tui3 in e5 sit-pai7 chhut-lai5, jip8 ti7 po2-huih sou2 siok8-hoe5 eng5-kng e5 tek-seng3.
Ku7-iok E5 Le7
“M7-bian2 kiaN, choe3 lin2 khia7-teh, khoaN3 Ia5-ho5-hoa kin-a2-jit8 ui7-tioh8 lin2 sou2 beh kiaN5 e5 chin2-kiu3;......Ia5-ho5-hoa beh ui7 lin2 kau-chian3, choe3 lin2 tiam7-tiam7, boh8 choe3-siaN” (Chhut Ai-kip8-ki3 14:13, 14). Siat-su2 tak8 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 ti7 leng5-seng3 e5 lou7-tou5, chit8-pou7 chit8-pou7 teh kiaN5 e5 si5, long2 oe7 kong2, kau-chian3 m7-si7 goa2 e5, si7 Siong7-te3 e5, an2-ni sit-pai7 kap tek-seng3 chiu7 oe7 hun chin beng5.
“Iok-su-a oa2-kun7 Ia5-li7-ko e5 si5 kiah8-bak8 khoaN3, khoaN3-kiN3 u7 chit8-lang5 chhiu2 puih8-to, khia7 ti7 i e5 tui3-bin7; Iok-su-a kun7-oa2 i, mng7 i kong2, Li2 si7 ui7 goan2 e5, a2-si7 ui7 goan2 e5 tui3-tek8 ah? I in3 kong2, Bo5, goa2 lai5 si7 choe3 Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 kun-tiuN2” (Iok-su-a 5:13,14). Iok-su-a hit si5 bo5 kong2: Kun-tiuN2, goa2 chin hoaN-hi2 li2 lai5, na7-si7 goan2 bo5 su-iau3 li2 e5 pang-chan7, goa2 u7 toa7-tin7 e5 kun-tui7, Ia5-li7-ko put-ko3 si7 chit8-e5 sio2-siaN5 na7-tiaN7, m7-bian2 lo5-hoan5 li2 goan2 ia7 oe7 kong-chhu2 i. Siat-su2 i na7 an2-ni kong2, Ia5-li7-ko siaN5 kiam2-chhai2 boe7 to2-hoai7. Chong2-si7 Iok-su-a kong2: “Goa2 e5 Chu2 beng7-leng7 lou5-pok8 sim2-mih8?” Kiat-ko2 Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 kun-tiuN2 u7 toa7 koan5-leng5, Chu2 e5 su3-chia2 chiong Ia5-li7-ko e5 siaN5-chhiuN5 phah to2 kau3 piN5-piN5.
Hian7-chai7, Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 kun-tiuN2 khia7 ti7 chia tui3 lan2 kong2: Li2 i2-keng sit-pai7, hit-e5 khoai3-khoai3 tiN5-poaN3 li2 e5 choe7 khah iaN5 li2, taN hou7 goa2 lai5 choe3, goa2 beh thoe3 li2 kau-chian3, hou7 goa2 choe3 li2 e5 Tek-seng3-chia2. Goa2 beh thoe3 li2 phah iaN5 tui3-tek8, hou7 li2 u7-hun7 ti7 chit-e5 tek-seng3. Li2 khoaN3, che kiam2 m7-si7 ki5-biau7 e5 su7 mah?
Goa2 Beh Chhiann2 Ia5-sou Khi3 Khui-mng5
U7 chit8 e5 sian-siN, mng7 chit8-e5 tit-kiu3 bo5 ku2 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 kong2: Hian7-chai7 Ia5-sou ti7 to2-loh8? I siuN7-liau2 chiu7 chhio3-chhio3 kong2: Ti7 goa2 e5 sim-lai7. Sian-siN koh mng7 i kong2: Siat-su2 bin5-a2-jit8 Sat-tan3 lai5 phah li2 e5 sim-mng5, li2 beh chaiN2-iuN7? I in3 kong2: Goa2 beh chhiaN2 Ia5-sou khi3 khui-mng5.
Li2 na7 iau2 m7-chai tek-seng3 e5 pi3-koat, Sat-tan3 eng7 goan5-lai5 e5 chhi3-tham3, eng7 khoai3-khoai3 tiN5-poaN3 li2 e5 choe7 lai5 phah li2 e5 sim-mng5, li2 it-teng7 oe7 koaN2-kin2 chau2-khi3 khui-mng5. Sat-tan3 tui3 so2-si5-khang khoaN3-kiN3 chiu7 am3-tiong hoaN-hi2, in-ui7 i2-cheng5 bat chin-choe7 pai2 khah-iaN5 li2, i chai-iaN2 chit pai2 ia7 oe7 koh khah-iaN5 li2. Li2 chiong mng5 khui chit8-phang7, kap i kong2-oe7, ti7 li2 iau2-ku2 teh siuN7 chiah-e5 chhi3-tham3 e5 si5, bo5 tiuN5-ti5 e5 tiong-kan, i e5 kha chiu7 tah8 jip8 mng5 lai5, choan5-sin ia7 long2 jip8-lai5, an2-ni, li2 chiu7 koh sit-pai7 lah.
Siat-su2 li2 i2-keng chai tek-seng3 e5 pi3-koat, Sat-tan3 lai5 phah li2 e5 sim-mng5, li2 chiu7 beh chhiaN2 Ia5-sou khi3 khui-mng5. Hit-si5 Chu2 beh kong2, Li2 thang tiam7-tiam7 toa3 chia, sin3-kho3 Goa2, Goa2 beh khi3 tui3-hu3 li2 e5 kiu5-siu5. Sat-tan3 tui3 so2-si5-khang khoaN3-tioh8 tak8 pai2 kau-chian3 long2 tek-seng3 e5 Ia5-sou beh lai5 khui-mng5, Sat-tan3 chiu7 koaN2-kin2 to5-chau2. Ia5-sou toa7 khui li2 e5 sim-mng5, khoaN3-kiN3 Sat-tan3 i2-keng chau2 khi3, chiu7 beh tui3 li2 kong2: Li2 i2-keng tek-seng3 lah. Hit si5 li2 beh chin gong5-ngiah8 kong2: Chu2 ah! Goa2 kan-ta che7 ti7 chia sin3-kho3 Li2 na7-tiaN7, goa2 long2 bo5 choe3 sim2-mih8, si7 li2 khah iaN5 i. Chu2 beh kong2: Tui3 taN i2-au7, li2 kap Goa2 an2-ni lai5 kau-chian3, li2 tiam7-tiam7 che7 teh, sin3-kho3 Goa2, Goa2 chiu7 chhut-khi3 kau-chian3, au7-lai5 tng2-lai5 chiu7 chiong tek-seng3 e5 kong-lo5 hou7 li2.
HiaN-ti7 chi2-be7, u7 lang5 thoe3 lan2 kau-chian3, che kiam2 m7-si7 eng5-kng koh ki5-biau7 e5 su7 mah? Ki3-jian5 u7 lang5 thoe3 lan2 kau-chian3, lan2 chiu7 boe7 tioh8-siong, kho2-sioh choe7-choe7 Ki-tok-tou5 bo5 beh an2-ni choe3, lan2 long2 ai3 ka-ki7 kap tui3-tek8 kau-chian3, bo5 ai3 hou7 pat8-lang5 thoe3 lan2 kau-chian3.
Khah-iaN5 Sat-tan3 e5, chi2-u7 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, Sat-tan3 na7 lai5 beh chhe7 li2, li2 tioh8 khi3 chhiaN2 I thoe3 li2 kau-chian3, Sat-tan3 chiu7 oe7 su. Chu2 thoe3 li2 kau-chian3, seng3-li7 chiu7-si7 li2 e5, li2 siuN7, kiam2 u7 pi2 che koh-khah ho2 e5 tai7-chi3 mah?
Chit Khoan2 E5 Seng-oah8 Kiam2 U7 Kho2-leng5 mah?
Ia5-sou Ki-tok u7 po2-siu2 li2 tit-tioh8 tiap8-a2-ku2 e5 tek-seng3, I kiam2 boe7 po2-siu2 li2 chit8 jit8, chit8 geh8-jit8 a2-si7 chit8 ni5 ku2 long2 tek-seng3 mah? Pi2-tek chu3-sin5 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, i chiu7 oe7 ti7 chui2-bin7 kiaN5, chong2-si7 i e5 bak8-chiu chit8-e7 li7-khui Ia5-sou, chiu7 tit8-tit8 tim5 loh8-khi3; na7-si7 i koh-chai3 chu3-sin5 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, i chiu7 oe7 thang koh ti7 chui2-bin7 kiaN5. Li2 na7 si5-siong5 kap Chu2 Ia5-sou choe3-hoe2, li2 chiu7 tak8-si5 long2 oe7 tek-seng3.
U7 chit8-e5 Seng3-si e5 chok-chia2 Hoai5-thek (Major Whittle), thak8 tioh8 Seng3-si Si-khek goa2 khiam3-eng7 Chu2, i chiu7 tit-tioh8 kam2-tong7 kong2, Tak8-si5 goa2 long2 khiam3-eng7 I. Au7-lai5, chiu7 koh sia2 chit8 siu2 Seng3-si Si5-si5 tit po2-siu2 ti7 I e5 thiaN3-thang3. Tioh8 si5-si5 tiam3 ti7 Chu2 Ia5-sou, li2 chiu7 oe7 chiaN5-choe3 chit8-e5 tek-seng3 e5 Ki-tok-tou5. Tit-tioh8 chit8-pai2 e5 tek-seng3 e5 keng-giam7, choat8-tui3 m7-si7 hou7 li2 tong3 kau3 kui-si3-lang5 .
Beh Chainn2-iunn7 Choe3?
Tai7-seng tioh8 ka-ki7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5, jin7 ke3-khi3 it-chhe3 e5 choe7, koh tioh8 thiat-ti2 hoan2-hoe2, in-ui7 Chu2 kong2: “Lan2 na7 jin7 lan2 e5 choe7, I si7 chin-sit8 kong-gi7, beh sia3-bian2 lan2 e5 choe7”. lang5 na7 jin7 choe7, chiu7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2; choe7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2 chiu7 tit-tioh8 soe2-chheng-khi3. “I e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou e5 huih soe2-tu5 lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7” (I Iok-han7 1:7). U7 oan5-choan5 koh thiat-ti2 e5 jin7-choe7, tit-tioh8 soe2 chheng-khi3 sia3-bian2 i2-au7, li2 chiu7 ho2-taN2 chiap-lap8 Ia5-sou Ki-tok choe3 li2 tek-seng3 e5 Chu2. Cheng5 li2 bat chiap-lap8 I choe3 Kiu3-chu2, taN tioh8 khui li2 e5 sim-mng5, chiap-siu7 I choe3 li2 tek-seng3 e5 Chu2.
I2-sek-lait8 peh-siN3 chhut Ai-kip8 liau2-au7, m7-na7 ke3 Ang5-hai2, koh tioh8 ke3 Iok-tan3-ho5. Li2 e5 tit-kiu3 chhin-chhiuN7 ke3 Ang5-hai2, chong2-si7 li2 tioh8 ai3 koh ke3 Iok-tan3-ho5-------chiu7-si7 tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8. Li2 u7 chiap-lap8 Ia5-sou Ki-tok choe3 li2 tek-seng3 e5 Chu2 mah? Kiam2-chhai2 li2 ti7 Chu2 e5 un-tian2 lai5 chin3-pou7, chong2-si7 tek-khak tioh8 u7 chit8-e5 chhut-hoat tiam2. Hoan7-su7 long2 u7 khi2-tiam2, li2 na7 bo5 khai-si2, chiu7 boe7 thang choe3 sim2-mih8. Tek-seng3 ia7 tioh8 u7 chit8-e5 khai-si2, hiu7-si7 li7-khui khong3-ia2 kau3 eng3-un2 e5 sou2-chai7; ia7 si7 tui3 sit-pai7 chhut-lai5 tah8 jip8 ti7 tek-seng3 e5 si5.
Li2 Na7 Sit-pai7 Beh Chainn2-iunn7?
Li2 khai-si2 kiaN5 thiN-lou7, siuN7 beh ke3 tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8, chong2-si7, u7-si5 kiam2-chhai2 koh-chai3 sit-pai7, hit si5 li2 chiu7 chin sit-chi3 kong2: Ko2-jian5 boe7 thang sit8-heng5, goa2 boe7 thang khah-iaN5.
Na7-si7 hiaN-ti7 chi2-be7, chit8-e5 khai-si2 teh oh8 kiaN5 e5 gin2-na2, siong5-siong5 oe7 poah8-to2. I boe7 to2 ti7 thou5-kha kong2: Bo5 lou7-eng7, goa2 khoaN3 pat8-lang5 teh kiaN5-lou7, na7-si7 goa2 chiu7 long2 boe7 hiau2 kiaN5. I oe7 khau3 chin thiam2, au7-lai5 beh koh khi2-lai5 kiaN5, i ia7 oe7 koh poah8-to2 kui2-na7-pai2, chong2-si7, kau3-be2, i chiu7 ka-ki7 oe7 kiaN5 lah.
I oh8 kiaN5 e5 si5 oe7 poah8-to2, in-ui7 i e5 kha iau2 nng2-chiaN2, bo5 lat8, tioh8 iong2-chong3 chiah oe7 kiaN5. Li2 siok8-leng5 e5 kha iau2 nng2-chiaN2, ti7 ke3-khi3 m7-bat kiaN5 tek-seng3 e5 lou7, sou2-i2 ti7 khi2-thau5 u7 poah8-to2 ia7 m7-thang loe2-chi3. Li2 u7 sin3 Ia5-sou choe3 li2 tek-seng3 e5 Chu2, tui3 Siong7-te3 jin7-choe7, kiu5 I sia3-bian2, chhiaN2 I pang-chan7, au7-lai5 koh khai-si2. Kiat-ko2, chiu7 boe7 koh poah8-to2 lah, ia7 in-ui7 Chu2 Ia5-sou tiam3 ti7 li2 e5 sim-lai7 teh oah8, li2 chiu7 chiaN5-choe3 chit8-e5 tek-seng3 e5 Ki-tok-tou5.
Li2 Thang Keng-ke3 Tek-seng3 E5 Seng-oah8
Tioh8 ki3-tit, li2 m7-bat u7 tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8, li2 ka-ki7 ia7 bo5 hoat-tou7, chi2-u7 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok bat keng-ke3 tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8. Na7 an2-ni, tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8 si7 sim2-mih8? Tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8 chiu7-si7 loe7-chai7 e5 Ki-tok, tui3 goa7-bin7 khoaN3 oe7 tioh8 e5 seng-oah8. I tui3 Seng3 Sin5 e5 koan5-leng5 lai5 tiam3 ti7 lan2 e5 sim-lai7, chiu7 tui3 lai7-bin7 oah8-chhut I e5 khoan2-sit, an2-ni, pat8-lang5 chiu7 oe7 khoaN3-tioh8 tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8. Li2 chiu7 chai, che m7-si7 ka-ki7 teh oah8, chiu7-si7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok tiam3 ti7 li2, thong-ke3 li2 teh oah8-chhut tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8. Che m7 si7 li2 ka-ki7 choe3 oe7 kau3 e5 seng-oah8, chong2-si7 I chiu7 oe7. Sou2-i2 tioh8 hou7 Siong7-te3 choe3 kang, hou7 I tiam3 ti7 li2 e5 lai7-bin7, che chiu7-si7 tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8.
“Chong2-si7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 , I hou7 lan2 tui3 lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok tit-tioh8 khah-iaN5”. Tit-tioh8 khah-iaN5 m7 si7 tui3 lan2 e5 lou2-lek8, hun3-tou3, khou2-chian3, si7 tui3 lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok lai5 khah-iaN5. Che si7 un-tian2, si7 le2-mih8, li2 boe7 thang than3 lai5 tit-tioh8, ia7 boe7 kham-tit tit-tioh8 e5, si7 I siuN2-su3 e5, tui3 Chu2 Ia5-sou siuN2-su3 hou7 lan2 e5. Li2 na7 siuN7 beh choe3 chit8 e5 tek-seng3 e5 Ki-tok-tou5, tioh8 chiap-lap8 I choe3 tek-seng3 e5 Kiu3-chu2, tioh8 hou7 I tiam3 ti7 li2 e5 lai7-bin7, siong5-siong5 ti7 ki5-to2, thak8 Seng3-keng kap Chu2 Ia5-sou kau-poe5. An2-ni kap I saN-tang5 kiaN5, I chiu7 beh thong-ke3 li2, hian2-beng5 I pun2-sin, che chiu7-si7 tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8.
Li2 u7 ai3 chit khoan2 e5 seng-oah8 a2-bo5? Na7 u7, tioh8 seng5-jin7 li2 e5 sit-pai7, chiap-lap8 Ki-tok choe3 li2 tek-seng3 e5 Chu2, hou7 I ti7 li2 lai7-bin7 thong-ke3 li2 oah8-chhut I eng5-kng koh tek-seng3 e5 seng-oah8.
